  "instructions": [
    "Preheat sous-vide machine to 145°F (63°C).",
    "Season the chopped chestnuts with salt and black pepper.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. Add the sliced red onions and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the minced garlic to the skillet and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chopped chestnuts to the skillet and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in the ground cumin, chili flakes (if using), and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Place the cooked sous-vide eggs on top of the chestnut mixture.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve with lemon juice on the side (if desired).",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
